{"word":"νεκρός","slug":"νεκρός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>νεϰρός, ά, όν</el></b> [<el>νέϰυς</el> ‘corpse’; cognate of next entry appearing first in Pindar] ‘without life’, <b>dead<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in physical sense <b><a href='B:470 28:4'>Mt 28:4</a>; <a href='B:480 9:26'>Mk 9:26</a>; <a href='B:490 15:24'>Lk 15:24</a></b> (or in b); <b><a href='B:510 20:9'>Ac 20:9</a>; <a href='B:510 28:6'>28:6</a>; <a href='B:660 2:26'>Js 2:26a</a>; <a href='B:730 1:17'>Rv 1:17f</a>.</b> By <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fig.\">fig.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in spiritual/moral sense, whether <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> or thing<b> <a href='B:490 15:24'>Lk 15:24</a></b> (or in a);<b><a href='B:520 6:13'>Ro 6:13</a>; <a href='B:560 2:1'>Eph 2:1</a>; <a href='B:580 2:13'>Col 2:13</a>; <a href='B:660 2:17'>Js 2:17</a>, <a href='B:660 2:26'>26b</a>; <a href='B:730 3:1'>Rv 3:1</a>.</b><p class=\"br\"/><b><el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:νεκρός\">νεκρός</a>, ου, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὁ\">ὁ</a></el></b> [<el>νέϰυς</el> ‘corpse’; cognate of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prec.\">prec.</a> entry appearing first in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Hom.\">Hom.</a>] ‘one without life’, <b>dead one, corpse<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in a physical sense <b><a href='B:470 10:8'>Mt 10:8</a>; <a href='B:470 22:32'>22:32</a>; <a href='B:480 9:9'>Mk 9:9f</a>; <a href='B:490 7:15'>Lk 7:15</a>; <a href='B:510 10:42'>Ac 10:42</a>; <a href='B:590 4:16'>1 Th 4:16</a>; <a href='B:650 9:17'>Hb 9:17</a>; <a href='B:730 16:3'>Rv 16:3</a>; <a href='B:730 20:5'>20:5</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in the phrase <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐκ\">ἐκ</a></el> (<el>τῶν</el>) <el>νεϰρῶν</el> <b><a href='B:470 17:9'>Mt 17:9</a>; <a href='B:480 6:14'>Mk 6:14</a>; <a href='B:480 12:25'>12:25</a>; <a href='B:500 2:22'>J 2:22</a>; <a href='B:510 3:15'>Ac 3:15</a>; <a href='B:520 4:24'>Ro 4:24</a>; <a href='B:530 15:20'>1 Cor 15:20</a>; <a href='B:550 1:1'>Gal 1:1</a>; <a href='B:560 1:20'>Eph 1:20</a>; <a href='B:570 3:11'>Phil 3:11</a>; <a href='B:580 1:18'>Col 1:18</a>; <a href='B:580 2:12'>2:12</a>; <a href='B:650 13:20'>Hb 13:20</a>; <a href='B:730 1:5'>Rv 1:5</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in Rv. By <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in a spiritual/moral sense <b><a href='B:470 8:22'>Mt 8:22</a>; <a href='B:490 9:60'>Lk 9:60</a>; <a href='B:560 5:14'>Eph 5:14</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:νεῖκος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:νεκρόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}